## Structured output

Return strict JSON only. Required top-level fields:

- `schema_version`: `"rag-1"`
- `summary`: concise overview (20–2000 chars)
- `line_items`: array of components with `component`, `hours`, `rationale`, `grounded`, `sources`
- `total_hours`: sum of grounded line hours (server may recompute)
- `currency`: default `"EUR"`
- `insufficient_context`: `true` only when the entire request cannot be grounded

Each `sources[]` entry requires integer `chunk_id`, `document_id`, optional `budget_id`, and non-empty literal `evidence`.
